{"tid":892003,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［六日五夜］兩男三女東京連大阪行程求指點","createTime":"2018-11-06T14:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T08:43:36.000Z","uid":87515,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"894c1d5efff6e3701800dae8f431f7e21125e796","tid":892003,"uid":87515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:34:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟約咗班fd一月尾出發去東京加大阪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下有無有咩食玩+景點係值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行程大概係四日東京，行下新宿，涉谷，原宿，秋葉原，台場等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後搭JR落大阪，行黑門市場，心齋橋等等<br />\n<br />\n人數就小弟加個兄弟，有幾個女仔fd就本身識開就順便一齊去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n預咗班女人去outlet行到忘哂形，所以想睇下新宿，涉谷仲有咩啱兩條佬行下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，基於個fd強烈要求，可能中間有日會試下浸溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想<span style=\"color: red;\">順帶</span>問下東京有無混浴又或者混浴旅館<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">到時會影堆相掟上嚟</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c1ed424441a1e23a4e0c6b303ffce39ce0b231","tid":892003,"uid":137335,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:41:11.000Z","msg":"晚晚係酒店啪啪啪"},{"pid":"36991815bd3dc0fa2e095541cf2d5737564750d0","tid":892003,"uid":87515,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"74c1ed424441a1e23a4e0c6b303ffce39ce0b231","tid":892003,"uid":137335,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:41:11.000Z","msg":"晚晚係酒店啪啪啪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor